	* lib/srfi-13/*.scm : fixed number of bugs
	* src/string.c, src/extlib.stub : removed redundant 'end' parameter
	  from Scm_StringSubstitute and string-substitute!
	* test/srfi.scm : finished tests for SRFI-13

